{"word":"G232 - ἁλιεύω - halieúō - hal-ee-yoo'-o - Go a-fishing","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἁλιεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">halieúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hal-ee-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Go a-fishing</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மீன் பிடி"},{"paragraph":"to fish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G231 - ἁλιεύς - halieús - hal-ee-yoos'/231\">G231</a>; to <i>be a fisher</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>fish:</i> - go a-fishing.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}